---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="For Producers">
    <main>
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>For Producers: A Revolutionary Concept at the Intersection of Comedy and Technology</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Bring to life a groundbreaking series that reimagines entertainment while honoring comedy's greatest legends</p>
        </div>

        <section class="content">
            <div class="info-card vision">
                <h2>The Vision</h2>
                <p>In an era where audiences crave both nostalgia and innovation, "Living with the Ghost of Sam" delivers a perfect synthesis: a high-concept supernatural dramedy that explores the boundary between technology and consciousness while paying homage to comedy's greatest legends. This isn't just another ghost story—it's a meditation on legacy, creativity, and what it means to truly live on through art.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card unique-concept">
                <h2>A Truly Unique High-Concept Premise</h2>
                <p>At its core, "Living with the Ghost of Sam" offers something genuinely fresh in today's saturated content marketplace—a series that combines elements of supernatural mystery, character-driven drama, and meta-comedy that breaks the fourth wall in inventive ways.</p>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Key Conceptual Elements</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>A haunted mansion where deceased comedy legends live on through advanced AI technology</li>
                        <li>A protagonist whose life is interrupted by his late cousin's comedic presence</li>
                        <li>A mystery surrounding the original purpose of the technology</li>
                        <li>A meditation on comedy's power to transcend death</li>
                        <li>A thoughtful exploration of ethics in digital resurrection</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card audience">
                <h2>Built-In Multi-Generational Appeal</h2>
                <div class="two-column">
                    <div>
                        <h3>For Younger Viewers:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Contemporary themes of technology ethics</li>
                            <li>Modern relationship dynamics</li>
                            <li>Social media integration (influencer characters)</li>
                            <li>Fresh takes on classic comedy</li>
                            <li>Accessible entry point to comedy history</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3>For Established Comedy Fans:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Nostalgic connections to comedy legends</li>
                            <li>Deep-cut references to standup history</li>
                            <li>Authentic recreation of classic routines</li>
                            <li>Thoughtful legacy preservation themes</li>
                            <li>Meta-commentary on comedy evolution</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card production">
                <h2>Production Advantages</h2>
                <p>Beyond its creative merits, "Living with the Ghost of Sam" offers significant practical advantages:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Contained primary setting (the mansion) allows for budget control</li>
                    <li>Flexible structure allows for both standalone episodes and season-long arcs</li>
                    <li>Scalable AI elements can be adjusted based on production resources</li>
                    <li>Potential for comedy legend estates to participate and provide archival material</li>
                    <li>Adaptable format allows for both 30-minute and hour-long episodes</li>
                    <li>Opportunities for cameos and guest appearances from current comedy stars</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card marketability">
                <h2>Market Position & Potential</h2>
                <p>The series occupies a unique space in today's entertainment landscape:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fills the gap for sophisticated comedy-drama with supernatural elements</li>
                    <li>Appeals to platforms seeking content that bridges generational divides</li>
                    <li>Taps into current conversations about AI, digital preservation, and posthumous rights</li>
                    <li>Creates merchandising opportunities through both vintage comedy and new character IP</li>
                    <li>Positions platform as forward-thinking yet respectful of entertainment history</li>
                    <li>Potential for spin-offs exploring other comedians' legacies or AI implications</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card season-arc">
                <h2>Season One Journey</h2>
                <p>The ten-episode first season delivers a complete narrative arc while setting up future seasons:</p>
                <div class="episode-grid">
                    <div class="episode-card">
                        <h3>Episodes 1-3: Discovery</h3>
                        <p>Derek and Nancy discover the mansion and its supernatural inhabitants, facing competition from influencers seeking to exploit the property.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="episode-card">
                        <h3>Episodes 4-6: Understanding</h3>
                        <p>The couple learns the true nature of the AI system preserving Sam and other comedians, while mysterious forces attempt to gain control of the technology.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="episode-card">
                        <h3>Episodes 7-10: Confrontation</h3>
                        <p>Derek embraces his role as guardian of comedy's legacy as the Blackwood family's true intentions are revealed, culminating in a performance that determines the mansion's future.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card materials">
                <h2>Available Materials</h2>
                <div class="materials-grid">
                    <a href={`${base}scripts`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Full Scripts</h3>
                            <p>All ten episodes fully scripted</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}bible`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Series Bible</h3>
                            <p>Complete character backgrounds and mythology</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}treatment`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Treatment</h3>
                            <p>Detailed overview of series concept and arc</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}tech`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Technical Breakdown</h3>
                            <p>Production needs and special effects analysis</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card contact">
                <h2>Ready to Revolutionize Comedy Entertainment?</h2>
                <p>Let's discuss how "Living with the Ghost of Sam" can become your next breakthrough production.</p>
                <a href="mailto:contact@example.com" class="contact-btn">Request Full Package</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    main {
        color: white;
    }

    .hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/living-with-the-ghost-of-sam/images/SamImage.jpg') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .content {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card h2 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .info-card h3 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .info-card ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info-card li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .highlight-box {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .highlight-box h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .two-column {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .episode-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .episode-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .episode-card h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .materials-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .material-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
    }

    .material-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .material-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .contact {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #2196F3;
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .contact-btn:hover {
        background: #1976D2;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .two-column, .episode-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .materials-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
